<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>501</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men huān xiào zhe jì xù, zǒu dào yī qǐ bù yào fēn lí,
 yǒu fēng yǒu yǔ shì cháng jiàn de, yǒu kǔ nán bù yào duǒ bì,
 yī tiān yī gè gù shì, zhī dào yuǎn shān yuǎn shuǐ de hán yì,
 lù zhǎng lù wān gāo gāo dī dī mó guǐ dōu jù pà hé yī,
 fú yīn méi yǒu guó jiè, zhēn ài yào dé zhe chóu dí,
 wǒ men huān xiào zhe jì xù quán rén lèi guī xiàng shàng dì.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men huān xiào zhe jì xù 迦南501</title>
</song>